    <div id="delete-modal" class="modal-overlay">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2>X√°c nh·∫≠n X√≥a</h2>
            <p>B·∫°n c√≥ ch·∫Øc ch·∫Øn mu·ªën x√≥a trang web n√†y kh√¥ng? H√†nh ƒë·ªông n√†y kh√¥ng th·ªÉ ho√†n t√°c.</p>
            <div class="modal-actions">
                <button id="confirm-delete-btn" class="btn btn-danger">X√≥a</button>
                <button id="cancel-delete-btn" class="btn btn-secondary">H·ªßy</button>
            </div>
